      • NORM_ERR_THRESH

        static final double NORM_ERR_THRESH
        Acceptable relative error threshold for all operations, a little greater than half of the least significant bit of the mantissa.
        More exactly, (2^-129) * 1.0005 == ~1.4693679e-39 * 1.0005 == 1.4701e-39
